WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.605
Men shunchaki Project Wizard yordamida Android Studioda yangi loyiha yaratdim.

00:00:04.605 --> 00:00:06.345
Men uni qurilmamda ishga tushirganimda,

00:00:06.345 --> 00:00:07.905
u, shunchaki, "Hello World" deydi .

00:00:07.905 --> 00:00:11.040
Hozir men onCreate metodini olib tashlamoqchiman.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:14.700
Men metodning e’lon qilinishidan boshlab

00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:18.960
ochish va yopilish qavslarigacha, shuningdek bu yerda 
bekor qilingan matnga qadar butun metodni tanlayman.

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.365
Qurilmada ilovani ishga tushiraman.

00:00:21.365 --> 00:00:24.705
Qiziq. Hozir, men ilova bo‘shligini ko‘ryapman. 

00:00:24.705 --> 00:00:26.670
"Hello world" matni yo‘qolib qoldi.

00:00:26.670 --> 00:00:30.600
Agar men bekor qilishni bossam, 
onCreate metodini yana ko‘rishim mumkin.

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:33.280
U bu metodni overriding qilish orqali paydo bo‘ladi,

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:36.865
biz aslida "Hello World" matni ekranda 
paydo bo‘lishiga olib kelmoqdamiz.

00:00:36.865 --> 00:00:40.300
Buning ma’nosi bor, chunki biz 
setContentView ni chaqirganimizda,

00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:46.055
u aslida asosiy XML joylashuv tartibi faoliyatni 
faoliyatning tarkibiy ko‘rinishiga sozlamoqda. 

00:00:46.055 --> 00:00:49.375
Shunday qilib, endi biz superklassda 
odatiy xatti-harakatlarni bekor qilish

00:00:49.375 --> 00:00:53.410
nima uchun foydali ekanligini tushunishni boshlaymiz.

00:00:53.410 --> 00:00:58.715
Biz onCreate usulini bekor qilsak, biz aslida 
biz xohlagan joylashuv tartibidan foydalanishimiz mumkin.

00:00:58.715 --> 00:01:02.040
Mayli, keling buni o‘chirib tashlaymiz.

